hock conditions. Finally, we find several locations along the\nrim, where spectra are significantly better explained (based on Bayesian\nevidence) by inclusion of the intermediate component, with a width of 180\nkms$^{-1}$ on average.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Jul 2017 19:56:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Aug 2017 11:38:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-25"}
